{
  "stem": "6924.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And-- and she knew somebody who knew that [INAUDIBLE] fuhrer for money.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We gave him three 20-- golden 20 pieces.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Three pieces, $20 bills.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And she arranged that I can leave the-- the camp, the Lackie, to the same place where Dina was in [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no, no, that's not the same.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This is two different men.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Dina knew somebody from the Judenrat who knew that-- that the-- that guy, that Wartzog who put me there in the first place.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he-- he had-- he arranged, you know, they should let me out from that camp and put me in that place where Dina was, in the [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That was-- that was not [INAUDIBLE] camp.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That was a normal place, a working place that you can-- we-- we slept there, but we can go out.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You know, we was-- it was normal working conditions.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 12 SECONDS] [SIGHS] [DRINKS]",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So when we came-- when we were together already, in that place, in the [NON-ENGLISH], I had an uncle that I mentioned before and my aunt.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But my aunt was born in [NON-ENGLISH], and she knew a lot of people.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I'd been in touch with her.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And she said that-- that we have to try to get out of here.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "She had a-- a person, two person, who was willing to hide us for-- willing to hide us for money.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And she made arrangements.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She-- she was with her husband.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She had a daughter.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "She-- the daughter was eight years old, Zusan.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "To get to that place.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "She wanted to take me along also.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But I told her that I have a girlfriend, Dina, and if she has to take me, she has to go with me.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "She was against it.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
